# Web3 Integration

Somnia Pumpaz integrates with the Somnia blockchain for wallet connectivity, smart contract interactions, and token management.

## Wallet Connection

- Web3 Provider: [src/components/web3Provider.tsx](mdc:src/components/web3Provider.tsx)
- Connect Button: [src/components/connectButton.tsx](mdc:src/components/connectButton.tsx)
- Connect Modal: [src/components/connect.tsx](mdc:src/components/connect.tsx)
- Wallet Component: [src/components/wallet.tsx](mdc:src/components/wallet.tsx)

## Smart Contract Integration

- Contract ABI and Address: [src/app/contracts/contract.ts](mdc:src/app/contracts/contract.ts)
- Main contract: `SOMNIA_PUMPAZ_ABI` and `SOMNIA_PUMPAZ_ADDRESS`

## Token Management

- Minting: [src/components/mint.tsx](mdc:src/components/mint.tsx)
- User account state: [src/redux/connection/userAccount.ts](mdc:src/redux/connection/userAccount.ts)
- Token state: [src/redux/connection/token.ts](mdc:src/redux/connection/token.ts)

## Libraries Used

- Web3 Libraries:
  - wagmi (v2.15.6)
  - ethers.js (v6.14.3)
  - viem (v2.31.0)
  - connectkit (v1.9.0)

## Smart Contract Functions

The Somnia Pumpaz smart contract includes functions for:

- Token management (ERC20 functions)
- Game mechanics (flip, rollDice)
- Staking (createStaking, claimStaking)
- User management (registerUser, verifyUserAddress)
- Referral system (getReferralDetails)
